## Embedded license metadata

Every skill file in the AI Enablement OS™ contains a `license:` field in its YAML frontmatter declaring the licensor and pointing to these terms. Releases delivered to specific buyers also contain a `licensee:` field identifying the licensed organisation. These fields are part of the licensed Materials. Removing, altering, or obscuring them constitutes a breach of this license.

